  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Dice Kingdoms is a multiplayer turn-based strategy game where each player must develop their island and compete for victory through culture, military conquest or building an expensive wonder.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/e54ba5869de4dc51097831430b6439a4.poster.avif?t=1712317784\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/e54ba5869de4dc51097831430b6439a4.webm?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/e54ba5869de4dc51097831430b6439a4.mp4?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Strategically prioritize what to build<br></li><li> Efficiently layout your city, anticipating attacks and diseases while optimizing for space</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/2032a16657c5c5e289651daf16f2eae7.poster.avif?t=1712317784\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/2032a16657c5c5e289651daf16f2eae7.webm?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/2032a16657c5c5e289651daf16f2eae7.mp4?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Build specialized houses to have more dice<br></li><li> Use rerolls to try to get the resources you need the most but risk natural disasters</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/aaebe2e18ef94e921f7c442c5e6d211f.poster.avif?t=1712317784\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/aaebe2e18ef94e921f7c442c5e6d211f.webm?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/aaebe2e18ef94e921f7c442c5e6d211f.mp4?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Automatic battles after choosing targets<br></li><li> Pillage of strategic buildings yields many resources<br></li><li> Use force to punish greedy development</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disasters</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/55189cf00a216da773c575e5f735eaa3.poster.avif?t=1712317784\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/55189cf00a216da773c575e5f735eaa3.webm?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501690/extras/55189cf00a216da773c575e5f735eaa3.mp4?t=1712317784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Natural disasters are determined by the number of skulls rolled<br></li><li> Some natural disasters affect yourself while some affect other players</li></ul>",
